(2, 1, '2011-03-13 07:53:57', '2011-03-13 07:53:57', 'This is an example page. It''s different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:\n\n<blockquote>Hi there! I''m a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my blog. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like pi&#241;a coladas. (And gettin'' caught in the rain.)</blockquote>\n\n...or something like this:\n\n<blockquote>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickies to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</blockquote>\n\nAs a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href="http://localhost/broodrblog/wp-admin/">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!', 'Sample Page', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'sample-page', '', '', '2011-03-13 07:53:57', '2011-03-13 07:53:57', '', 0, 'http://localhost/broodrblog/?page_id=2', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(4, 2, '2011-04-13 01:37:34', '2011-04-13 01:37:34', 'Hello World Wide Web!\r\n\r\nIf you''re reading this, congratulations - you''ve just stumbled upon  the best kept secret the world has probably just started to hear about.  Broodr.com has just launched (somewhat officially) and although we have a  long road ahead of us (filled with coffee fueled hackathons, invention  road trip competitions, and intense animatronic robot battles)¬† - we''re  happy you''ve decided to come along for the ride. Right now we are  allowing the first 500 people who decide to upload free and unlimited  accounts. After a week or two we will soon open up the check out system  to anyone in the world - so you can begin purchasing items (which is  kind of important too!)\r\n\r\nOur goal with Broodr is to build the best community for entrepreneurs  and inventors of all kind. What are we looking for - the most unique,  coolest, and hardest to find items in the world. So, without further ado  - start uploading your products, browse the marketplace, and share the  site with your friends, family, and even foes.\r\n\r\nThanks and look for some killer updates coming soon!\r\n\r\nJason', 'Welcome to Broodr.com', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'welcome-to-broodr-com', '', '', '2011-07-01 14:19:28', '2011-07-01 14:19:28', '', 0, 'http://broodr.com/blog/?p=4', 0, 'post', '', 5),
