(14, 2, '2011-05-19 19:56:04', '2011-05-19 19:56:04', 'Hey World Wide Web,\r\n\r\nWe are excited to let everyone know that we are in the midst of completing a major update. As of today, buyers on Broodr can now check out with a credit card!¬† You can still use your PayPal account but this system now allows another option for purchasing items.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://broodr.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/Screen-shot-2011-05-19-at-3.57.13-PM.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-17" title="PayPal Update" src="http://broodr.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/Screen-shot-2011-05-19-at-3.57.13-PM.png" alt="" width="572" height="372" /></a>\r\n\r\nThis is a big deal.\r\n\r\nBe excited.\r\n\r\nCatch Phrase!\r\n\r\nJason', 'Broodr Now Accepts Credit Cards', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'broodr-now-accepts-credit-cards', '', '', '2011-07-01 14:19:25', '2011-07-01 14:19:25', '', 0, 'http://broodr.com/blog/?p=14', 0, 'post', '', 2),
(12, 2, '2011-04-30 01:51:30', '2011-04-30 01:51:30', 'We are proud to announce that Broodr.com was recently a winner of  a major business competition in New York State, taking home a big first  prize trophy in our division (and some money too!)\r\n\r\nThe prize money we have been awarded will be specifically used to update the site and  make sure Broodr continues to grow at this amazing pace. We hope through your feedback and  continual support we can create some cool new features, provide  customization and support tools, and overall improve the functionality  of the entire site.\r\n\r\nIt''s only been days since we''ve officially gone live so thank you to those who have already uploaded and we look forward to more amazing work from all potential sellers.\r\n\r\nPlease make sure to follow us on Twitter  for more frequent updates: @Broodr\r\n\r\nGeneric catch phrase!\r\n\r\nJason\r\nFounder and CEO', 'Taking home the Gold!', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'taking-home-the-gold', '', '', '2011-07-01 14:19:26', '2011-07-01 14:19:26', '', 0, 'http://broodr.com/blog/?p=12', 0, 'post', '', 1),
