ive caps are incorporated into the design, many serving as the feet for the characters so you wouldn‚Äôt even know that it‚Äôs a flash drive. The figures are also smaller than the average flash drive you would buy in stores.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<iframe width="480" height="390" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/lh5nScxvC5g" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>\r\n\r\nEach device is personalized and made to your order, so you never receive stock products. With these unique characters, you will not mix up or misplace your USB again.\r\n\r\nImpress your friends as you connect a super cool LEGO¬Æ creature to your computer and still have the same amount of space, 4GB-8GB, as the boring, solid-colored flash drives that you used before.\r\n\r\nRe-connect with your inner child and make work fun! The artistic possibilities do not stop when you receive your own <em>Databrick</em> USB. You can add on to the USB flash drive and expand with your own LEGOs to personalize your gadgets.<a href="http://broodr.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/Screen-shot-2011-07-01-at-9.45.20-AM.png"><img class="size-full wp-image-72 alignleft" title="Screen shot 2011-07-01 at 9.45.20 AM" src="http://broodr.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/Screen-shot-2011-07-01-at-9.45.20-AM.png" alt="" width="532" height="307" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nPrices range from $69.95 to $249.95 depending on how elaborate your flash drive may be. Delivery takes an estimated 4-5 weeks. Order now at Broodr.com\r\n\r\nFind more information about Stefan‚Äôs creations and purchasing procedures at <a href="../../seller/store/85">http://broodr.com/seller/store/85</a>\r\n\r\nNote: LEGO¬Æ does not endorse or sponsor these products.', 'The Friday Review: Databrick', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '70-revision-21', '', '', '2011-07-01 14:15:56', '2011-07-01 14:15:56', '', 70, 'http://broodr.com/blog/?p=96', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
