(98, 1, '2011-05-27 14:23:52', '2011-05-27 14:23:52', 'We are very excited to announce that Broodr HQ is moving to New York City this summer!¬† The company has been accepted into the General Electric - OMD 2011 Incubator program where we will begin working starting this June.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://broodr.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/GE1.jpg"><img class="size-full wp-image-24 alignleft" title="GE1" src="http://broodr.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/GE1.jpg" alt="" width="137" height="89" /></a> <a href="http://broodr.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/OMD-and-Strap-line1.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-26" title="OMD-and-Strap-line" src="http://broodr.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/OMD-and-Strap-line1.jpg" alt="" width="269" height="78" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nThis Incubator acceptance is a well timed opportunity to help us grow the business and to bring new media and marketing campaigns to life. We should also note that the Broodr team is also growing! We are fortunate to have brought on several key interns and a PR rep to help build key relationships early on for the company and to continue improving the design and functionality of the actual website.\r\n\r\nAnnouncement #3?: Broodr has passed well over 200 products from 14 different countries. Thanks everyone for your awesome support - 500 is coming soon!\r\n\r\nWell, that''s about it really... Onwards and Upwards!\r\n\r\nNot sure if that''s actually a catch phrase, but you get the idea.\r\n\r\nJason\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Moving to NYC!', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '22-revision-21', '', '', '2011-05-27 14:23:52', '2011-05-27 14:23:52', '', 22, 'http://broodr.com/blog/?p=98', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
