(14, 'seller', '<h1>Selling On Broodr</h1>\n<p>Whether casual or your career depends on it, selling and sharing your products is a hassle-free process. We use a sophisticated PayPal system to ensure customer satisfaction, and make sure you get paid immediately when an order is placed. At Broodr we like helping people spread their dreams - that''s why you''re here, right? Help us build the community now &ndash; upload sell and your work today.</p>\n<div class="row2">\n<h1>What To Sell?</h1>\n<img title="seller" src="../../../themes/user/images/img-what-to-sell.jpg" alt="seller" width="860" height="376" /></div>\n<h1>Not Allowed</h1>\n<p>Here is our list of things you are not allowed to sell on Broodr: Machine Guns, Smutty Magazines, Live Animals, Human Hair, Mold, and Apples. Everything else is pretty much fair game. (Disclaimer: Broodr does not allow the selling of products that violate U.S. Federal Laws nor does not fall under ownership of their creator. All products sold must comply with Broodr Terms of Agreement or Copyright Policy).</p>\n<div class="row2">\n<h1>How It Works</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Sign up below and confirm your PayPal email</li>\n<li>Fill out your profile and list a product or two to submit your account for approval</li>\n<li>Once approved, your listings become active for sale</li>\n<li>When you make a sale you''ll get paid instantly, minus Broodr''s 5% fee</li>\n</ul>\n</div>', 0, '2011-03-12', '', 1),
