(26, '', 'Hallo :-),\n\nthank you that you are interested in my handmade Highspeed USB 2.0 products in original Lego¬Æ Bricks / Plates and Minifigures.\n\nFirst of all i like classic design, Lego¬Æ :-) and technic. So i tought it would be a nice idea to bring all my interests together .\n\nSome technical details:\nI offer handmade usb products in original LEGO¬Æ Bricks/Plate and Figures.\nYou will not get products in stock because every product will be made after your order.\nMy personal standard is very high so you always get the maximum possible quality.\n\nAll products are custom made by me and almost every used item is a original Lego¬Æ product (brick/plate/knob/minifig).\n\nAll products are made with professional tools in west germany by myselfe in my sparetime.\n\nFor more informations please visit my website www.databrick.de\n\nIf you have a question .. please ask me.\nMy email: info [!at] databrick.de\n\nIf you want the newest info just follow me on twitter:\nhttps://twitter.com/databrick\n\nLEGO¬Æ Brick and Knob configurations are trademarks of the LEGO¬Æ group of companies, which does not sponsor, authorise or endorse this website or products.\n\nregards\nStefan\n', 85, '2011-04-14', 'about', 0),
