(33, '', 'Payment \nPayPal is currently the only method of payment accepted in the shop - you do not need a PayPal account to use PayPal. You can pay with a credit card on PayPal.\n\nShipping\nWe ship worldwide & use expedited international insured shipping service. If you have special shipping requests, we will be happy to apply.\n\nThe kozo lamps ship from Israel and produced on demand (after order + payment ). Please allow up to 14 days for production & handling before the shipment.\n\nPackaging\nIn an effort to reduce waste, packaging materials are reused, repurposed or reusable. We encourage you to ask for the same eco-friendliness in all your actions. Little changes = BIG difference!\n\nOrder confirmation\nAfter you place your order, we confirm the order details and shipping address with you before we ship the lamp.\nPlease make sure that you check your E-mail.\n\nDocuments\nKozo lamps arrive with safety and handeling instructions.\nPlease read them carefully, for your safety.\n\nWarranty\nThe kozo lamps come with a 24 months warranty for all the electric components. The lamps get fully checked for functionality and quality before shipping. If the lamp gets to you severely damaged, we will gladly replace it after we are contacted (up to 7 days from when you receive the lamp) and the original purchase is returned via reputable carrier of your choice with Delivery Confirmation.\n\nWe take pride in designing high quality and unique products and offer good customer service. we hope that you will be pleased with your order. \n\nRefunds\nAll sales are final as each lamp is handmade and produced for you after you have placed an order, therefore we cannot cancel the order or issue a refund. If you are not 100% happy with your order we''ll do everything we can to make things right for you. Please exercise good judgment before placing your order and ask any questions you may have. We happily will respond promptly.\n\nPrivacy\nAll the shipping details and information that we recieve from you remains confideltial. No one else has any access to your e-mail or information.\nThe money transfered via paypal is secured and we do not have any access to your account details or means of payment at any time.', 95, '2011-04-17', 'policy', 0),
(34, '', 'Kozo Lamp genuine lighting brand\nHandmade by Anat & David Shefa - Two designers from Israel. The kozo lamps were born in 2008 and are being sold since then to customers all around the globe.\n\nDesigning the kozo lamps\nOur world is flooded with industrial materials, waiting for a chance to be Upcycled or Repurposed and become a lot more than what we know of them. By using an unexpected material to describe everyday objects we achieve a new- "out of the box"- design and get a chance to tell a different story...\n\nThe kozo lamps are made out of galvanized iron pipes and fittings, handmade by us at our design clinic. The raw material maintains the authentic spirit of the design, rough and vivid. Galvanized iron is rust free, but it also ages a bit at the edges and joints where the metal is exposed, the result is a slight peaceful touch of beautiful rust, exposing its age. \n\nEach kozo lamp has a unique innovative faucet light switch, giving it the authentic and fun side of design. \n\nGalvanized iron = zinc coated iron\nIt does not rust and can last for many years without any need of treatment. By using the galvanized material we save any additional coating process or color appliance. It preserves the unique quality of the material, achieving a complete and honest design for the kozo lamps.\n\nStandards & regulations\nThe kozo lamps are developed with a professional electronics engeneer that is part of the R&D team. Each lamp contains high quality electric components with standard certificate of approval. wiring is heat resistant and isolated. All the components are tight and secured making the lamp stern, safe and reliable.\n\nWe take pride in the durability and quality of the kozo lamps and our goal is to provide high standard products with good service and attitude and to bring light & joy to everybodys life!\n\nIn our designs we strive to give new life and meaning to the materials that we use, always keeping it on the green side. Our basic attitude is to manufacture less. We don''t mind using ready-made where we can, giving a credit to someone else and manufacturing less, thus saving the world additional unnecessary production.\n\nWe go the extra mile to produce environmentally responsible, long lasting products. It is our policy to refrain from going commercial - so by designing effective, happy, handmade, and non-commercial objects, we give more to the world and take less.\n\nThank you for choosing to invest your time in exploring our designs. We love you! ', 95, '2011-04-17', 'about', 0),
(35, '', 'I accept Paypal only. \nPlease contact me if there are any problems, and to work out a solution.', 96, '2011-04-17', 'policy', 0),
(36, '', ' I live in the mountains of Central Pennsylvania where the Pine Creek Valley meets the Susquehanna.  I love making things that make people smile :)', 96, '2011-04-17', 'about', 0),
(37, '', '<p id="internal-source-marker_0.8790033785548307" style="margin: 0pt 7.75pt 0pt 7pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Verdana; color: #333333; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">5 O''clock Shadow knows what it''s like to have a chilled noggin on a brutal day. Sometimes that coat collar just isn''t enough. That''s why we''ve created totally awesome </span><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: Verdana; color: #333333; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">bearded face masks</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Verdana; color: #333333; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">. They have it all; </span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Verdana; color: #333333; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">efficiency</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Verdana; color: #333333; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;"> in the cold, </span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Verdana; color: #333333; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">versatility</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Verdana; color: #333333; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;"> with any head gear, and </span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Verdana; color: #333333; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">handmade</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Verdana; color: #333333; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;"> by women who are mistaken for men all too often.</span></p>\n<p><br /><br /></p>\n<p style="margin: 0pt 7.75pt 0pt 7pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Verdana; color: #333333; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">5 O''clock Shadow beards are hand knitted with a cotton-polyester backing for comfort and two elastic straps for stability. The Shadow gives superior protection against the elements along with that kick in the face you''ve always wanted.</span></p>\n<p><br /><br /></p>\n<p style="margin: 0pt 7.75pt 0pt 7pt; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Verdana; color: #333333; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">5 O''Clock Shadow beards come in multiple sizes, weights, and colors. Please see our website for more of these options.</span></p>\n<p style="margin: 0pt 7.75pt 0pt 7pt; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Verdana; color: #333333; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">five-oclockshadow.com</span></p>\n<p style="margin: 0pt 7.75pt 0pt 7pt; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Verdana; color: #333333; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">facebook.com/5oclockshadows</span></p>\n<p style="margin: 0pt 7.75pt 0pt 7pt; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Verdana; color: #333333; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;"><br /></span></p>\n<p style="margin