(38, '', '<p><span style="color: #000000; font-family: Verdana; font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Verdana; color: black;">We accept PayPal for payment. PayPal accepts credit cards, funds from bank accounts, and wire transfers.&nbsp;<span style="color: #000000; font-family: Verdana; font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Verdana; font-size: small;">All items listed are brand new in original manufacturer''s packaging unless otherwise indicated, therefore we do not accept refunds. However, if you receive an item that is either not what you ordered or damaged, please contact us immediately after delivery for replacement. We want you to be 100% satisfied with your purchase!!</span></span></span></span></p>', 105, '2011-04-26', 'policy', 0),
(39, '', '<p class="toptext" style="text-align: center;"><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><span style="font-size: medium;">A promotional item that is both functional and practical!</span></span></p>\n<p class="btmtext" style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: medium;">With the rapid growth </span><br /><span style="font-size: medium;"> of people drinking and carrying </span><br /><span style="font-size: medium;"> bottled water... we finally have a small, easy to use, </span><br /><span style="font-size: medium;"> yet inconspicuous holder for this extremely large untapped market.</span></p>\n<p class="btmtext" style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: medium;">Accommodates various size bottles, </span><br /><span style="font-size: medium;"> cups and soda cans.</span></p>\n<p class="btmtext" style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: medium;">Easily attaches to your waistband or belt. </span><br /><span style="font-size: medium;"> Clips on similar to a cell phone holder.</span></p>\n<p class="btmtext" style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: medium;">Ideal for charities and fundraisers, </span><br /><span style="font-size: medium;"> corporate and trade show give-aways.</span></p>\n<p class="btmtext" style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: medium;">Elastic webbing is perfect for logos and </span><br /><span style="font-size: medium;"> promotions. </span><br /><span style="font-size: medium;"> Fits in a pocket or purse when not in use!</span></p>\n<p class="btmtext" style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="color: #0099ff;">http://holdyourwater.net/<br /></span></span></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>', 108, '2011-04-26', 'about', 0),
(40, '', '<p>I welcome custom orders! If you have something in mind *that is similar to my other work* but doesn''t quite match what I have listed in my shop, please let me know. I''d be happy to make you exactly what you desire. But these types of orders do take longer..<br /><br />Thanks woodguy</p>\n<p>I take pride in the quality of my work and do my best to ensure my items are of the highest craftmanship and descriptions accurately reflect the item. If, however, you are dissatisfied for any reason, just let me know within 7 days of receiving your item and we can work out arrangements for exchange or refund. (I am unable to refund shipping charges, sorry.)</p>\n<p><strong>woodguy32 - hotrodworks.net - oldtimecomputer.com does not take responsibility for the installing these products to your computer, ipad, iphone, ipod or any other electronic device, you will need to understand how to operate and install such products..</strong></p>', 82, '2011-04-26', 'policy', 0),
(41, '', '<p>Inventist Inc. dreams, designs, and develops all of our products in-house.&nbsp; The inventions spread across a variety of fields all with one goal in mind, too provide people with fun, new, and interesting products.&nbsp; </p>', 106, '2011-04-27', 'about', 0),
(42, '', '<p>We accept Paypal payments.&nbsp; Every item is made with great care and attention to detail. &nbsp;If for some reason you find you are not happy with an item please contact us right away.&nbsp; A full refund of the original purchase price and shipping paid is offered if you return the item to us in its original condition within 10 business days (buyer pays return shipping).</p>', 113, '2011-04-27', 'policy', 0),
(43, '', '<p>We love mixing the old fashioned art of knitting with modern technology by making hand knit cozies for things like iPhones.&nbsp; Lovingly crafted and stylish cases for your gadgetry are our specialty.</p>', 113, '2011-04-27', 'about', 0),
(44, '', '<p>We have been selling on eBay for about 7 years.</p>\n<p>We have shipped our various items to worldwide with thousands of satisfied customers.</p>\n<p>We are trust worthy and reliable.</p>\n<p>Please feel free to contact us everytime if you have a question.</p>\n<p>Enjoy shopping with us.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 112, '2011-04-27', 'about', 0),
(45, '', '<p>We accept only paypal payments.</p>\n<p>We are responsible if you don''t receive the item.</p>', 112, '2011-04-27', 'policy', 0),
(46, '', '<p>Dream Cheeky Ltd was established in 2008, but we''ve been supplying customers with the gadgets they need to harass coworkers since 2005. Our mission is to constantly introduce highly inventive and contemporary products that creatively utilize the interaction between computer software and firmware driven devices and have high play value and depth.</p>', 80, '2011-04-27', 'about', 0),
(47, '', '<div class="row clear">\n<h2>Payment</h2>\n<p>PayPal is the safest and quickest way to buy from our site.<br /> We accept checks and money orders made out to Tecoart, LLC and will ship once funds are cleared.<br /> <br />&nbsp; Email us or call us 941-545-7602 after ordering item and let us know you are mailing check/money order.<br /> <br /> Our correspondence address is:<br /> TEcoArt, LLC<br /> 6474 Watercrest Way, Suite 401<br /> Lakewood Ranch, FL 34202-5240</p>\n</div>\n<div class="row clear">\n<h2>Shipping</h2>\n<p>We ship Hard Drive and Circuit Board Clocks via USPS Priority Mail to all States and Countries. Tracking notices are sent to the buyer''s email.<br /> <br /> Larger items such as Apple iClocks and Vintage Clocks only ship to the USA and go via UPS Ground. <br /> <br /> Please Email us if you are a non-USA country to get a shipping quote for any iClock or Vintage Clock.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="row clear">\n<h2>Refunds and Exchanges</h2>\n<p>Refunds and exchanges will be made for damages incurred in shipping. We will issue a RMA upon notification by email or phone. sales@tecoart.com or (941) 545-7602</p>\n</div>', 114, '2011-04-29', 'policy', 0),
(48, '', '<p><span style="font-size: small;">Think gifts, awards or rewards with our cool clocks, office clocks, retro clocks, teacher gifts, hard drive, Apple and circuit board clocks, vintage and rare clocks all from recycled computers! Batteries are always included. We ship USPS Priority Mail, so it gets to you quickly! ALL OUR ITEMS ARE READY TO SHIP!</span><br /> <br /><span style="font-size: small;"> NBC/Thrillist featured TEcoArt Clocks in a video. Google "NBC Tecoart Video" to view. </span><br /> <br /><span style="font-size: small;"> The ** New York Daily News ** chose our Metallic Blue Hard Drive Clock as their featured recycled item for Earth Day 2010!</span><br /> <br /><span style="font-size: small;"> Mashable.com chose TEcoArt for their article "10 Excellent Examples of Recycled Gadgetry" sponsored by Best Buy, April 2010.</span><br /> <br /><span style="font-size: small;"> TEcoArt was chosen by America''s Best Magazine for inclusion in their annual "Hot List 2008, Green Goods." Each time you choose one of our unique and unusual clocks we have just recycled together.</span><br /> <br /><span style="font-size: small;"> Each clock comes with a "Certificate of Authenticity" signed by the artist. TEcoArt, recycling computer parts to clocks since January 2007. </span></p>', 114, '2011-04-29', 'about', 0),
(49, '', '<p>Greetings, nerds, geeks and video game freaks! I am the inventor of hand-poured glycerin soaps that look like all your favorite gadgets.<br /><br />Thank you for visiting DigitalSoaps!&nbsp;<br /><br />My name is Chrystal Doucette, and I started DigitalSoaps in January 2009 on a whim. Before soap, my passion was journalism. I earned a Bachelor of Arts Degree in journalism in 2005, and a Master of Arts Degree in communication in 2008. I am 26 years old.&nbsp;<br /><br />When I was younger, my dad took me to Computer City. A trip highlight included the chocolate 5.25-inch floppy disks the store sold. With a desire to relive my past, I checked online to see if anyone still sold the chocolate disks. I didn''t find any. But during my research, I found plenty of chocolate molds shaped like electronics. This discovery sparked the idea of making soap. I was already a fan of handmade soap, so the two ideas merged well.<br /><br />My first video game-themed soap, a PlayStation 2 replica controller, received so much attention, I decided to start making more video game controller replicas. I was able to leave the 24-7 world of news reporting for a more empowering existence.&nbsp;<br /><br />When you buy a soap from me, you are supporting a small business and you are supporting the original artist of these types of soaps. Geek soap has been my job since November 2009.&nbsp;</p>', 119, '2011-04-30', 'about', 0),
(50, '', '<p>Please pay by PayPal, money order or personal check. I ship after I receive payment. I will cancel your order if I do not receive payment within 10 days of your order, unless you contact me.</p>\n<p>I refund or replace damaged products. I ship to PayPal addresses only. So if you need your item shipped to a different address, send me a specific message. Thank you.</p>\n<p>A wholesale price list is available by e-mailing Chrystal@cleangeeks.com</p>', 119, '2011-04-30', 'policy', 0),
(51, '', '<p>Welcome to&nbsp;our shop.<br /><br />I hope you enjoy having a browse through the BlackGizmo range of contemporary designs.<br /><br />We deals mainly in wood products.Design and new product development.<br /><br />All our products are hand made in our own workshop in Estonia.</p>', 121, '2011-05-01', 'about', 0),
(52, '', '<h2>Shipping</h2>\n<p>All of our products is made on order and are 100% handmade.<br />This means that dispatch could take up to 1 week. <br />Your order will be sent within 5 working days after the payment. <br />You will receive a shipping tracking code when we ship the goods.</p>\n<h2>Refunds and Exchanges</h2>\n<p>If You are unhappy with any item from BlackGizmo store, You can return it for a full refund less postage and transaction fees. Simply return the item to us in brand new condition including in tact packaging within 7 days of receiving.<br />We ask that You first email us with Your order number and product name so we can process Your return correctly. We value Your opinion, and are always striving to offer the very best so please let us know exactly why You are not happy with it.</p>', 121, '2011-05-01', 'policy', 0),
(53, '', '<p><strong>INFO</strong><br /> <br /> Hi, I''m a Canadian new media artist with a formal background in electrical engineering. While also engaged in painting, audio, and video practices, it is sculptural lighting which has drawn the focus of my creative energy. This work has been supported by the Ontario Arts Council, the City of Ottawa, and the Corel Endowment Fund for the Arts.<br /> <br /> I''ve exhibited widely in Ontario and contribute to Ottawa&rsquo;s cultural community through board and volunteer involvement with artist run centres such as Artengine, Galerie SAW Gallery, and SAW Video; and have been involved with New York based art/technology centres NYC Resistor and Eyebeam </p>\n<p>I often work with my wife, Deborah, as a DJ/VJ duo or for other lighting and artistic projects, collaborating as "The Latest Artists."<br /> <br /> Thanks for checking out my shop here on Broodr!</p>\n<p><strong>LINKS</strong></p>\n<p>Personal site featuring art and music projects:<br /> www.aomalley.org<br /> <br /> Blog focused on electronic music and arts:<br /> www.technoetc.net/blog<br /> <br /> Flickr:<br /> www.flickr.com/aom<br /> <br /> Vimeo:<br /> www.vimeo.com/LatestArtists<br /> <br /> The Latest Artists (DJ/VJ duo):<br /> www.TheLatestArtists.com</p>', 110, '2011-05-04', 'about', 0),
(54, '', '<p><strong>SHIPPING</strong></p>\n<p>While I keep a small inventory of designs in stock, works may need to be built to order, and will ship 1-2 weeks after placing your order. I can confirm specific shipping times once you''ve placed an order, or feel free to contact me in advance.</p>\n<p>For items eligible for international shipping, you will be charged the highest shipping rate during checkout and I will refund the shipping difference of the actual shipping cost.</p>\n<p>My shipping preferences are Canada Post, then couriers such as UPS or FedEx. If available, I will provide you with a tracking number once your order has shipped.<br /> <br /> In Canada and the US, shipping times are 4-8 business days, while international orders are around 6-10.<br /> <br /> If you are an international customer, please contact me since you may also require a different power supply.<br /> <br /> While I try to ship to avoid taxes or duties for international orders, I cannot be response for additional expenses incurred at customs.</p>\n<p><strong>REFUNDS / EXCHANGES</strong></p>\n<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Assembled items</span><br /> <br /> Should you not be satisfied with your purchase, I offer a full refund, less shipping, within 15 days of delivery. Please contact me before making a return.<br /> <br /> In the unlikely need of repair due to faulty workmanship or unexpected component failure within 2 years of purchase, I will repair your work free of charge; after 2 years, repairs will be accommodated at a reasonable rate. Shipping to me for repairs is your responsibility while I''ll cover the return shipping.<br /> <br /><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Kits</span><br /> <br /> Should you not be satisfied with your purchase, I offer a full refund, less shipping, within 15 days of delivery, but this applies only to un-assembled kits; unfortunately I CANNOT offer a refund for kits that have been partially or fully assembled by the buyer. Please contact me before making a return.<br /> <br /> Since I cannot control the assembly of kits, I cannot warrant faults due to workmanship. I can however support issues that are a result of component failure. Feel free to contact me regarding issues with kits that you have assembled. Support will be accommodated on a case-by-case basis.</p>\n<p><strong>COMMISSIONS</strong><br /> <br /> I''m always open for commissions, so feel free to get in touch to discuss your bright ideas!<br /> <br /><strong> CONTACT ME</strong><br /> <br /> Please don''t hesitate to contact me through this site with any questions or if you''d like additional documentation of any of my work.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 110, '2011-07-20', 'policy', 0),
(55, '', '<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: small;">They consist of specially designed high fidelity speakers that can be inserted into a comfortable headband. They sound great and feel fantastic. Halo Headphones can be used anywhere, whether you are walking, running or training at the gym. And because they are so comfortable, you can even wear them while sleeping!</span></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: small;">Take the high fidelity speakers and insert them into the opening at the back of the headband. Unlike other headphones, the speakers are not fixed in place, so you can align them directly over your ears for the best sound quality and maximum comfort.</span></p>\n<ol style="text-align: center;">\n<li><span style="font-size: small;">Make sure the speakers face the inside of the headband</span></li>\n<li><span style="font-size: small;">Slip the speakers through the opening at the back of the headband</span></li>\n<li><span style="font-size: small;">Put the headphones on &amp; align the speakers over your ears.</span></li>\n</ol>\n<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>', 129, '2011-05-13', 'about', 0);
