(56, '', '<p>All Sales are final unless I grossly misrepresent my products.&nbsp;&nbsp; I try to post as many pictures as possible so that you will know exactly what you are buying.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>I use flat rate shipping in the United States.&nbsp; I will ship abroad, but please email me for a quote.</p>', 107, '2011-05-15', 'policy', 0),
(57, '', '<p>Hi, my name is Kodykoala and I make video game related figures and statues.&nbsp; I have been doing it for about 3 years as a hobby, and I have just recently started to sell my creations.&nbsp; If you are interested in seeing more of my creations, please visit my website:</p>\n<p>http://www.kodykoala.com</p>\n<p>If you have any questions, please email me at:</p>\n<p>donald.c.kennedy2@gmail.com</p>', 107, '2011-05-15', 'about', 0),
(58, '', '<p>Welcome to 8-Bit Memory! Relive the good old days of video gaming with our unique re-purposing of all those old 8-bit classics.&nbsp;<br /><br />All our sales are custom built to your specifications. Any hard drive size from 500GB up to 1 TB is available, and any game you can imagine can be used for the enclosure. We can also turn any of your old favorites into an awesome desk clock or mouse pad!&nbsp;<br /><br />Please contact us for pricing. Please include the game and hard drive size in your request. Prices may vary depending on the rarity of the game requested. Since all parts are custom ordered, please allow 5 to 7 business days for shipping. Please allow 1 to 3 business days for shipping for clocks and mous pads. Additional time may be required if the game requested is not in stock. Contact us for a quote and a custom order!</p>\n<p>Payment is expected immediately after the order is placed. If you need more time to complete payment, please feel free to contact me prior to placing the order to make arrangements. If payment is not made within 7 days after purchase and the buyer fails to contact me to make arrangements, the transaction will be canceled, negative feedback will be left, and the item will be re-listed. Payment is accepted through PayPal only.</p>\n<p>Warranty Information:<br /><br />Toshiba offers a 3 year warranty on all their hard drives, and we are pleased to extend this warranty to our customers. In the event of a hard drive failure, contact us for replacement details. PLEASE back up your data! Data recovery is NOT COVERED under this warranty. If your hard drive is removed from the enclosure, it is NOT COVERED under this warranty. If you have issues with your hard drive, please contact me immediately for repair or replacement. Do not remove the drive yourself.&nbsp;<br /><br />Unfortunately there is no warranty available for the USB drives. Clocks have a 6 month warranty on defective components.</p>\n<p>All photos in all listings are stock photos, and are not necessarily representative of the condition of the hard drive enclosure you will receive. We try very hard to get games of the best quality, but some wear and tear should be expected. If you have questions about the condition of the game we will be using for a specific listing or would like photos of that game, please contact us PRIOR to placing your order.</p>', 75, '2011-05-24', 'policy', 0),
