(84, '', '<p>Rare beasts is a small electronics design lab in Canberra, Australia.</p>\n<p>We build a range of electronic goods, but we are focused on hand held electronic musical instruments. The instruments we design, we also use in our own bands to make music.</p>\n<p>Rare beasts started in 2007 as a part time business selling musical gadgets that we played in our own bands, in 2009 Rare beasts started full time to put more energy into new designs and making popular items available for sale again. All of the items you will find in our store are 100% designed by us, and 100% handmade. So its all about fun, good quality materials, natural products, circuit bending, and new ideas.&nbsp;</p>', 166, '2011-07-22', 'about', 0),
