(86, '', '<p>Twisplays are one-line LED signs. They are 26" long X 4" high X 1.5" deep. They weigh approximately 3 lb.</p>\n<p>Twisplays need to be plugged in to an electrical outlet. The Twisplays adapter/converter can handle 110V-220V and comes with a typical USA plug. For shipments outside the USA, you may need to supply your own electrical plug connector.</p>\n<p>Twisplays come with mounting brackets and can be screw-mounted on a wall or mounting board or hung from a screw, nail or hook (from a wall or ceiling).</p>\n<p>Twisplays can rest upright on a table, desk or shelf &ndash; or placed on a floor or table-top display stand.</p>\n<p>Twisplays currently only come in a black casing with scrolling text in alternating colors.</p>\n<p>Twisplays must be connected to a PC via Serial port or USB connection. Twisplays have a built in Serial port connector but come with a Serial-to-USB adaptor for connection to a USB port for your convenience. You can display one or more Twitter streams of your choice.</p>\n<p>Twisplays are meant for indoor use only. Please contact us concerning your outdoor needs.</p>\n<p><strong>Shipping</strong><br />As a special introductory offer, we are currently shipping to Europe for $40.</p>\n<p>Please contact us for distribution and delivery outside the USA, Canada and Europe.</p>\n<p><strong>Return Policy</strong><br />Full refund (not including shipping) when undamaged product is returned within 30 days.</p>', 173, '2011-07-25', 'policy', 0),
