(420, 228, 'EXO6 iPhone 4 Case in Silver Aluminum', 79.00, 12.00, '', 'iPhone4,iPhone case,cell phone case,phone case,metal case', 15, '<p>The aluminum EXO6 case is both lightweight and durable. It has an elegant tech look and fits the iPhone 4 like a glove. Your phone will not rattle around or move within the case. This case is made for those who prefer to purchase something more durable, lasting and elegant, than your run of the mill phone case. Its designed to show you notice, enjoy and care about fine design and craftsmanship.<br /><br />Our cases are made from two pieces of solid aluminum stock, which we carefully mill and finish by hand. They are then anodized- a process that renders the aluminum harder, stronger and scratch resistant. We offer a clear anodize which showcases the look of the raw aluminum, while still providing a hard, scratch resistant finish, a deep black anodize that really highlights the iPhone&rsquo;s touch screen, and a nice middle gray which is a unique color that is "the new black". The EXO6 is secured with 5/64" hex head screws at all 4 corners, ensuring that the case will be protected even in the worst falls. <br /><br />All openings and switches are readily accessible through the EXOvault case. We guarantee the fit of all Apple brand iPhone chargers and headphones (the white ones that came with your iPhone.) We cannot guarantee the fit of all third party accessories. We can guarantee all your friends will be jealous.<br /><br />This case comes in a plain-back version and an engraved version. See additional models here in on Broodr or refer to my website http://exovault.com/shop.html.</p>', 1, '2011-06-22', 148, 15, ',,,promotion,', '<p>We make all of our cases according to order. We handcraft everything right here in our shop and pay attention to every detail. Quality takes time, and we will usually be able to create your iPhone case and ship it to you with in 2 weeks. Of course many orders, especially those in the US will be delivered much faster than that.</p>\n<p>We ship pretty much anywhere in the world. In the USA we use Priority Mail from the US Post Office and you will be able to track your package. In the USA the shipping rate is 12.00. Of course we will combine shipping on more than one case.</p>\n<p>We can use Priority Mail International for most of Europe, Canada and Japan (and some additional countries) no problem, the cost is 22.00. For some countries like Italy, Mexico, regions throughout the Middle East, Russia, Hungary and other areas of Eastern Europe we suggest you upgrade to Fed Ex or pay for trackable Express shipping via the US Post Office which will cost you 36.00. Fed Ex, UPS, DHS and others are available but range in price from 50 - 90.00 depending on country.</p>', 1, 1),
