(151, 68, 'Roll-Up Drum Kit', 29.99, 10.00, 'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aX1wYD_xXd8', 'Dream Cheeky,usb gadget,instrument,drum,usb drum', 50, '<p>Who cares if you are tech support or middle management... you deserve to experience the thrills of a Rock &amp; Roll lifestyle. You also deserve a raise and a vacation, but we can''t help you there. What we''ll do instead is offer you this roll-up drum kit that plugs into your USB port and lets you wail away, pretending to be someone that matters!</p>\n<p>The Roll-Up Drum Kit includes six different pad areas (snare, kick &amp; two toms). Simply install the included software, plug your kit in, and let your seemingly talented fists-of-fury fly. Choose between 50 percussion sounds, 20 preprogrammed percussion sets and 100 preprogrammed beats. If you&rsquo;re a n00b, ''learning mode'' lets you play along to some pre-recorded beats. Otherwise, just enjoy the &lsquo;free play&rsquo; mode. You can also record your riffs and save to a wave file.</p>\n<p>Flexible drum mat</p>\n<p>Includes 2 drumsticks and&nbsp;custom software for Windows</p>\n<p>Powered by USB with 4'' cable</p>\n<p>Dimensions: 13" x 8"</p>\n<p>Compatible with: Windows 7 / Vista / XP SP2 or later</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 1, '2011-04-28', 80, 5, ',distributor,funding,promotion,', '<p>- In stock orders normally ship within 24 hours, if placed on a business day. For orders placed on the weekend, please allow up to 3 days.</p>\n<p>- All parcels are shipped using Hong Kong Registered Air Mail and will arrive in 7 to 10 business days.</p>\n<p>- Please contact customerservice@dreamcheeky.com with questions concerning your order.</p>\n<p>- For large quantity orders, please contact sales@dreamcheeky.com.</p>', 1, 1),
