(163, 64, 'Hand Knit Nintendo Dsi - Ds Lite - 3Ds Cozy in Gra', 22.00, 1.95, '', 'nintendo 3ds,ds lite,dsi,case,gray', 1, '<p>This rainy gray cozy is the perfect fit for your Nintendo Ds Lite, Dsi, or 3Ds. Knit with in cable and stockinette stitches that hug the game system and provide tactile appeal. A pocket for games has been added to the back and should fit about 3 games inside. Handmade matching rainy gray pom pom and pink felt hearts adorn the cozy for added cuteness. <br /><br />This cozy measures approximately 4" by 6". Knitted circularly for a virtually seamless fit with just a single seam at the base of the cozy. Free gift wrap available upon request!</p>', 1, '2011-04-28', 113, 8, ',,,,', '<p>We ship within 24 hours of receiving your payment. Shipping is USPS First Class mail as it is a very affordable rate for the customer and still gets your knitted item there in a reasonable amount of time. If you need the item faster please let us know and we will happily ship via Priority Mail.</p>', 1, 0),
(164, 101, 'Weight Loss Leg Slim Half Sole Slipper Shoes', 12.99, 9.99, '', 'weight loss,slippers,slim leg,shoes,women', 10, '<p><span style="font-size: small;">- Slip these Leg Slim Slippers on to help you lose weight and tone your legs</span><br /><span style="font-size: small;">- Just put these Leg Slim Slippers on while you are walking, standing, cooking, doing household chores</span><br /><span style="font-size: small;">- You will gradually see results if you just use them 3 times a day for fifteen minutes each time</span><br /><span style="font-size: small;">- Exercise you leg muscles</span><br /><span style="font-size: small;">- Massage the reflexology zones on your feet</span><br /><span style="font-size: small;">- Burn more calories while walking or standing</span><br /><span style="font-size: small;">- Easy to use! Get rid of cellulite efficiently</span><br /><span style="font-size: small;">- Leg Slim Slippers help to break down excess fats of your leg, help get rid of fats faster</span><br /><span style="font-size: small;">- Adjustable so that fits for most lady and women''s sole is 9cm in width</span><br /><span style="font-size: small;">- Material: polyester and nylon</span></p>', 1, '2011-04-28', 112, 3, ',,,,', '<p><span style="font-size: small;">Please allow 3-4 weeks for the whole packaging, shipping, customs and delivery.</span></p>', 1, 0),
(438, 57, 'Xing Body Toner', 29.95, 12.00, 'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5LhQLjQN46k', ',,,,', 100, '<p><span style="font-size: small;"><strong>Pump rubber. Not iron.</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: small;">The Body Toner gives you an efficient, effective and affordable way to work out every major muscle group, right in the comfort of your own home.</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: small;">Work your abdominals, biceps, triceps, deltoids, pectorals, back, quadriceps, hamstrings, glutes, abductors, adductors and calves.</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: small;">The adjustable rubber tubing makes it perfect for all levels of workouts. And because of the compact design, the Body Toner is one of the most portable and lightweight exercise products available. You can even take it with you when you travel, to the gym, or your workout buddy''s house. Wherever you feel most comfortable working out, the Body Toner can come right along with you.</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: small;">Regardless of your workout level, the Body Toner is made for everyone. As you progress, you can customize the Body Toner to fit your necessary resistance level. A manual and instructional DVD are included. So stretch your physical limits with rubber, not iron. Get the Body Toner.</span></p>', 0, '2011-06-28', 106, 10, ',,,,', '<p><span style="font-size: small;"><strong>Return Policies </strong></span><br /><span style="font-size: small;">Inventist, Inc. is dedicated to customer satisfaction. If your purchase does not fulfill your needs for any reason, you can return your item for an exchange or refund. Simply contact our store to receive instructions on returning your purchase. The following conditions apply:</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style="font-size: small;">All returns must be made within 30 days of purchase.</span></li>\n<li><span style="font-size: small;">Items returned unused will be fully refunded (except for shipping).</span></li>\n<li><span style="font-size: small;">Items returned used will be refunded 70%.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style="font-size: small;"><strong>Shipping Policies</strong> </span><br /><span style="font-size: small;">Shipping to and from Inventist.Inc. is at the customer''s expense and varies according to weight, size, shipping type and location.&nbsp;</span></p>', 1, 0),
(210, 61, 'SOAP PlayStation game controller glycerin soap', 5.50, 3.00, '', 'PlayStation,Geek,Soap,PS3,PS3', 10, 'Zomg! Waking up at noon has never been so exciting. <br />This listing is for a replica soap of a PlayStation video game controller, scented with Energy fragrance oil! <br /><br />This is a bright, yet sweet citrus scent. It is my new favorite fragrance selection. <br />When I opened my shop I made this style of soap, along with a bunch of other gadget soaps. The response this one received is what started my further invention of a full line of video game controller soaps. This is the soap model that started the geekery soap revolution. <br /><br />This color PlayStation soap was featured in Gee Magazine! <br /><br /> Just to note, the soap is flat rather than shaped like a controller all 360 degrees. It is also smaller than an actual controller. It weighs more than four ounces. For the full size version of the PlayStation controller, see my shop! <br /><br />A great gift for PlayStation addicts or children in need of a wash. <br /><br /> Made by the original creator of video game controller and electronics soaps, DigitalSoaps. <br /><br />I vow to continue providing you with the latest and greatest gadget soaps in my Level 3 quest to drench the gaming community with awesome cleanliness! <br />This product is vegan. <br /><br />Ships worldwide!<br /><br />The soap contains the following ingredients:<br />&middot;        Coconut Oil<br />&middot;        Palm Oil<br />&middot;        Safflower Oil<br />&middot;        Glycerin (kosher, of vegetable origin)<br />&middot;        Purified Water<br />&middot;        Sodium Hydroxide (saponifying agent)<br />&middot;        Sorbitol (moisturizer)<br /><br />About DigitalSoaps and founder Chrystal Doucette:<br />I invented soap shaped like video game controllers and other electronics on a whim. My soap is the first to communicate with subcultures of gamers and geeks. I haven''t seen anything like it and I haven''t seen gamers this excited about soap.<br /><br />When I was younger, my dad took me to Computer City. <br /><br />A trip highlight included the chocolate 5.25-inch floppy disks the store sold. With a desire to relive my past, I checked online to see if anyone still sold the chocolate disks. I didn''t find any. But during my research, I found plenty of chocolate molds shaped like electronics. This discovery sparked the idea of making soap. I was already a fan of handmade soap, so the two ideas merged well.<br /><br />My first video game-themed soap, a PlayStation 2 replica controller, received so much attention, I decided to start making more video game controller replicas. I was able to leave the 24-7 world of news reporting for a much more zen existence. When you buy a soap from me, you are supporting a small business and you are supporting the original artist of these types of soaps. <br /><br />Each product is made in my home. I remain committed to using only high quality, vegan ingredients in my soap.<br /><br />You can find my soaps covered in Computer idee (Netherlands), GamePro, GamesMaster (German), GEE Magazine (German), Forbes.com, Micro Hebdo (French) Wired UK, WonkaVision. Photos of the articles can be viewed at: http://www.facebook.com/pages/DigitalSoaps/205525062068?v=photos&amp;ref=ts#!/album.php?aid=226187&amp;id=205525062068&amp;ref=pb<br /><br />Your soap comes shrink wrapped for freshness and gift giving. Thank you!<br /><br />I HAS A SOCIAL NETWORK:<br />http://twitter.com/DigitalSoaps<br />www.facebook.com/pages/DigitalSoaps/205525062068<br />or me : http://www.facebook.com/chrystal.doucette', 1, '2011-05-01', 119, 15, ',,,,', '', 1, 0),
(196, 63, 'Wooden Office lamp', 136.00, 17.00, '', 'led,lamp,table,wooden,light', 2, 'Hand made wooden Office lamp.<br />DL003<br />Add a distinctive modern accent to your home or work office desk with this eye-catching and efficient LED desk lamp. <br />Head contains 30 powerful LEDs while only uses 7,2 - watts of electricity, saving you costs on electricity. <br />LEDs use a fraction of the power (80-90%) required by conventional filament bulb <br />LEDs can withstand shock, vibration, frequent switching and extremes without compromising its long life.', 1, '2011-05-01', 121, 11, ',,,,', '<div align="left">Ready to dispatch in: 3-5 working days after receipt of payment</div>', 1, 0),
