(213, 242, 'Custom Gameboy with Back-light and pro-sound modif', 90.00, 7.00, 'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ALZH_V8IWyw', 'gameboy,8bit,chiptune,lofi synth,video games', 3, '<div id="tab_description" class="tab_page" style="display: block;">\n<p>I will build you a Gameboy DMG-01 from scratch. This price includes a back-light color of your choice and prosound modification.</p>\n<p>...Super bright dual led back-light allows for composing in the dark and great for live shows. also include an internal 1/8" stereo line out for better sound with less hum and more bass. the speaker still works and original headphone output still work.</p>\n<p>!!This price includes Grey DMG case, Back light of your choice, and Pro sound modification... however,</p>\n<p>Many Back-light colors, custom paint, and button combination''s available. (pictured is original DMG with blue back-light and nes controller buttons)</p>\n<p>...pitch kits also available for an extra fee</p>\n<p>(video is of pitch bent version)</p>\n</div>', 1, '2011-07-26', 74, 5, ',distributor,funding,promotion,', '<p>To US ships via Flat rate priority box, International ships via First Class</p>', 1, 0),
