(463, 57, 'Macdec', 135.00, 69.00, '', ',,,,', 99, '<p><span style="font-size: small;">Click your wireless apple keyboard and your apple magic trackpad into the thodio MacDec and enjoy your mac as efficient and ergonomically as a MacBook Pro, on your desk or while lounging on your couch or easy chair</span>.<br /><br /><span style="font-size: small;"> The thodio MacDec is machined out of 15mm solid nutwood or transparent acrylic in the shape of a MacBook Pro 15" and comes equipped with 4 transparent rubber bumpers to provide a solid grip on your desk or lap. The keyboard and trackpad will stay in place with 8 powerful neodymium magnets, to provide you with a solid and secure platform to control your mac with.</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: small;"><strong>technical specifications:</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: small;">- material: 15mm CNC machined nutwood or acrylic</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: small;">- dimensions: 36.4 x 24.9 x 1.5 cm</span></p>\n<ul></ul>\n<p><span style="font-size: small;"><br /></span></p>', 0, '2011-07-07', 103, 15, ',,,,', '', 1, 0),
(215, 160, 'AquaSkipper', 495.00, 35.00, 'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=g9bmLv6iUj4', ',,,,', 25, '<p>The AquaSkipper&rsquo;s patented design, hydrofoil wings and fiberglass spring let you fly across the water by hopping up and down. The secret to your awesome power?&nbsp;Hydrofoil wings have very little drag in the water.&nbsp;Plus, the aircraft aluminum frame weighs a mere 26 pounds.&nbsp;So take on the surf. Try new tricks.&nbsp;Race your friends. And turn heads everywhere you ride.</p>\n<p>When the fun is done, quickly stow your AquaSkipper in the optional tote bag.</p>\n<p>It''s environmentally-friendly. No noise pollution.&nbsp;No air pollution.&nbsp;No water pollution.&nbsp;No engine.&nbsp;And with the AquaSkipper, the only fuel you&rsquo;ll burn are the calories from an exhilarating and invigorating cardiovascular workout.</p>\n<p>The AquaSkipper has been featured nationally on The Today Show on CBS, MTV&rsquo;s Parental Control, Discovery Channel''s MythBusters, I Want That! on HGTV, Beyond Tomorrow, and The Price is Right, and was a semi-finalist in the History Channel&rsquo;s Modern Marvels Invent Now Challenge in 2007. It has done extremely well in Australia and Europe, where it was recognized with an international award for new sport-related inventions at ispo BrandNew in Munich, Germany.</p>\n<p>Like us on Facebook at www.facebook.com/inventistinc and follow us @inventistinc on Twitter.</p>', 1, '2011-05-02', 106, 8, ',,,,', '<p>&nbsp;All items will be shipped within 2 business days.</p>\n<p><input id="gwProxy" type="hidden" /><!--Session data--><input id="jsProxy" onclick="if(typeof(jsCall)==''function''){jsCall();}else{setTimeout(''jsCall()'',500);}" type="hidden" /></p>\n<div id="refHTML">&nbsp;</div>\n<p><input id="gwProxy" type="hidden" /><!--Session data--><input id="jsProxy" onclick="if(typeof(jsCall)==''function''){jsCall();}else{setTimeout(''jsCall()'',500);}" type="hidden" /></p>\n<div id="refHTML">&nbsp;</div>', 1, 0),
