(650, 14, 'Kymera Wand remote control', 79.00, 10.00, '', 'wand,remote,magic,,', 100, '<p class="p1">The world&rsquo;s first real magic wand &ndash; the first motion-sensitive, buttonless universal remote control, shaped like a wizard&rsquo;s wand.</p>\n<p class="p1">- Inside the wand&rsquo;s ancient-looking exterior beats a heart of pure science fiction.</p>\n<p class="p1">- With just a flick of the wrist, you can control almost any TV, DVD, set-top box, hi-fi, or pretty&nbsp;much any equipment that uses a regular infra-red remote control.</p>\n<p class="p1">- 13 movement gestures allow the wand to perform 13 magical functions (with each function&nbsp;emulating one button from a regular remote control).</p>\n<p class="p1">- Learns from your existing remote controls.</p>\n<p class="p1">- Presented in a red silk brocade-lined gift box with a black faux-dragonhide covering.</p>\n<p class="p1">- Batteries included</p>', 1, '2011-08-01', 179, 5, ',,,,', '<p>We''re a UK-based company but hold stock in Chicago, IL for shipping to our US customers via FedEx. &nbsp;Deliveries to all other countries are shipped from the UK via Royal Mail airmail.</p>', 1, 0),
(437, 20, 'Alkacharger', 99.97, 12.00, '', ',,,,', 100, '<p><span style="font-size: small;"><strong>The perfect way to recharge, organize and store batteries at the same time.</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: small;">Start saving today on battery costs with the AlkaCharge, the only battery charger on the planet that can recharge up to 34 regular Alkaline type cells at once.</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: small;">The AlkaCharger holds up to 6 D cells, 6 C cells, 10 AA cells, 10 AAA cells, and 2 9V batteries. On average, the money saved by using the AlkaCharger is about 75% of the batteries'' cost. Storing batteries in the AlkaCharger will recharge them between uses, so your batteries will always be charged and ready.</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: small;">The clean design of the AlkaCharger also makes it an attractive and convenient way to keep your batteries organized in one place. If you''re tired of poking around in drawers and cupboards looking for stray batteries - only to find that half the time they are dead - this product is for you!</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: small;">&nbsp;The AlkaCharger is featured in the following catalogs: Potpourri Group, QCI, and Sporty&rsquo;s Catalog, as well as on our website at <a href="http://www.inventist.com/alkacharger">www.inventist.com/alkacharger</a>.</span></p>', 0, '2011-06-28', 106, 15, ',,,promotion,Licensee', '<p><span style="font-size: small;"><strong>Return Policies </strong></span><br /><span style="font-size: small;">Inventist, Inc. is dedicated to customer satisfaction. If your purchase does not fulfill your needs for any reason, you can return your item for an exchange or refund. Simply contact our store to receive instructions on returning your purchase. The following conditions apply:</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style="font-size: small;">All returns must be made within 30 days of purchase.</span></li>\n<li><span style="font-size: small;">Items returned unused will be fully refunded (except for shipping).</span></li>\n<li><span style="font-size: small;">Items returned used will be refunded 70%.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style="font-size: small;"><strong>Shipping Policies</strong> </span><br /><span style="font-size: small;">Shipping to and from Inventist.Inc. is at the customer''s expense and varies according to weight, size, shipping type and location.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 1, 0),
(317, 59, 'GameCube Desktop Organizer - Platinum', 33.00, 7.00, '', 'Nintendo,Office,Desk,Organizer,', 2, '<p><span style="font-size: small;">Get major geek cred at work with these desktop organizers hand-crafted from recycled Nintendo GameCubes. </span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: small;">FEATURES:</span><br /><span style="font-size: small;">*The faceplate now pulls forward to reveal a hidden drawer.</span><br /><span style="font-size: small;">*The Power and Reset buttons have been drilled out for pencil/pen slots.</span><br /><span style="font-size: small;">*Inside the disk bay, the optical drive has been replaced with a storage tray.</span><br /><span style="font-size: small;">*Side vents have powerful magnets installed for paperclip storage.</span><br /><span style="font-size: small;">*The rear handle has a shelf installed so that phones, ipods, or other small devices can be nested inside the handle.</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: small;">COLORS:</span><br /><span style="font-size: small;">Three colors are available:</span><br /><span style="font-size: small;">Indigo w/ Green Drawer </span><br /><span style="font-size: small;">Black w/ Purple Drawer </span><br /><span style="font-size: small;">Platinum w/ Blue Drawer (You now are on this listing.)</span><br /><span style="font-size: small;">If you prefer a different color combination, use the "Order Custom Item" option.</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: small;">DON''T HESITATE:</span><br /><span style="font-size: small;">Quantities are dependent on the availability of broken systems, so I cannot guarantee that more of any color will be available. </span></p>', 0, '2011-05-25', 118, 8, ',,,,', '', 1, 0),
