e, Wide Band </span></div>', 0, '2011-05-17', 129, 5, ',,,,', '', 1, 1),
(247, 95, 'Recycled Computer Hard Drive Clock with Video Card', 40.00, 8.00, '', 'video card,hard drive clock,unique gift,geek clock,desk accessory', 1, '<p><em><span style="font-size: small;">&ldquo;Oh yeah&hellip;awesome clock!&rdquo; -- Jarret</span></em><br /><br /><span style="font-size: small;">Unique <strong>handcrafted one-of-a-kind clock</strong> was an actual desktop computer''s 3.5" drive recycled to now, spin the time.</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: small;">Dial is actual hard disk platter with original mirror finish with brass hour and minute hands and coordinated black second hand.</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: small;">The clock''s base was the disk drive''s protective cover that has been custom painted a metallic "eco-green" finish.</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: small;">A piece of its video/graphics card circuit board further accents the clock''s base.</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: small;">Approx. 5" wide by 6.5" tall.</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: small;">Artist signed and numbered "Certificate of Authenticity."</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: small;">Ready for the home or office, quite a striking conversation piece!</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: small;">Golden raised numbers (12-3-6-9 positions) can be added for free if desired. Contact us immediately after purchasing and we''ll make the change. </span></p>', 1, '2011-05-09', 114, 15, ',,,,', '<div id="cboxLoadedContent" style="display: block; width: 840px; overflow: auto; height: 86px;">\n<div id="shipping-popup">\n<p><span style="font-size: small;">We ship <strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">USPS Priority Mail with Tracking Number</span></strong>. We ship first thing in the morning day after order.&nbsp; We ship the same way for International Orders unless First Class Mail is requested.&nbsp; First Class Mail does not have Tracking Number.</span></p>\n</div>\n</div>', 1, 0),
(248, 113, 'Striking Original Black Casing Hard Drive Clock', 36.00, 8.00, '', 'hard drive clock,geek gift,fathers''s day,geek clock,desk clock', 1, '<h1><em><span style="font-size: small;">"We rescued another hard drive from becoming e-scrap."</span></em></h1>\n<p><span style="font-size: small;"><em>&ldquo;Form + function = this clock is awesome!&rdquo; -- El Tigre</em><br /><br />This hard drive clock is quite striking and is a wonderful example of recycling.<br /><br />Natural black and aluminum casing with the hard drive''s actual circuit board controller serving as the base, very cool.<br /><br />Dial is actual hard disk platter with mirror finish and golden raised numbers.<br /><br />Brass hour and minute hands and a contrasting black double-wave second hand complete this awesome clock.<br /><br />Actual desktop computer''s 3.5" drive transformed to spin the time.<br /><br />Artist signed and numbered "Certificate of Authenticity."<br /><br />Approximate size 4" wide by 6" tall.<br /><br /></span><span style="font-size: small;">This clock would look great on the desk or as a gift or as a company award. </span><em><span style="font-size: small;"><br /></span></em></p>', 1, '2011-05-09', 114, 5, ',,,,', '<div id="cboxLoadedContent" style="display: block; width: 840px; overflow: auto; height: 86px;">\n<div id="shipping-popup">\n<p><span style="font-size: small;">We ship <strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">USPS Priority Mail with Tracking Number</span></strong>. We ship first thing in the morning day after order.&nbsp; We ship the same way for International Orders unless First Class Mail is requested.&nbsp; First Class Mail does not have Tracking Number.</span></p>\n</div>\n</div>', 1, 0),
(316, 64, 'GameCube Desktop Organizer - Indigo', 33.00, 7.00, '', 'Nintendo,Office,Desk,Organizer,', 2, '<p><span style="font-size: small;">Get major geek cred at work with these desktop organizers hand-crafted from recycled Nintendo GameCubes. </span><br /> <br /><span style="font-size: small;">FEATURES:</span><br /><span style="font-size: small;">*The faceplate now pulls forward to reveal a hidden drawer.</span><br /><span style="font-size: small;">*The Power and Reset buttons have been drilled out for pencil/pen slots.</span><br /><span style="font-size: small;">*Inside the disk bay, the optical drive has been replaced with a storage tray.</span><br /><span style="font-size: small;">*Side vents have powerful magnets installed for paperclip storage.</span><br /><span style="font-size: small;">*The rear handle has a shelf installed so that phones, ipods, or other small devices can be nested inside the handle.</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: small;">COLORS:</span><br /><span style="font-size: small;">Three colors are available:</span><br /><span style="font-size: small;">Indigo w/ Green Drawer (You now are on this listing.)</span><br /><span style="font-size: small;">Black w/ Purple Drawer </span><br /><span style="font-size: small;">Platinum w/ Blue Drawer</span><br /><span style="font-size: small;">If you prefer a different color combination, use the "Order Custom Item" option.</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: small;">DON''T HESITATE:</span><br /><span style="font-size: small;">Quantities are dependent on the availability of broken systems, so I cannot guarantee that more of any color will be available. </span></p>', 0, '2011-05-25', 118, 8, ',,,,', '', 1, 0),
(281, 83, 'Banksy Apache Vinyl Macbook Decal', 14.00, 3.00, '', 'Banksy,Laptop,decal,Macbook,Apache', 5, '<p>Apache Laptop Decal. Inspired by world renowned graffiti artist Banksy.&nbsp; The decals are not limited to laptops, they can be applied to any smooth surface, for example fridge, door, or even your car.<br /><br /> Our decal stickers are precision cut from our high grade self adhesive vinyl. For more banksy designs please check out our other listing<br /><br /> Application instructions are available from the links above.<br /><br /><strong>Size:22x13</strong></p>', 1, '2011-05-18', 135, 1, ',,,,', '<p>Your decal will be packaged between two solid pieces of cardboard. It will include a practice decal to get used to the application process. Since we are based in New Zealand sometimes the decals can take up to two weeks to arrive, but trust me they are well worth the wait.</p>', 1, 0),
(285, 60, 'Banksy Girl with Red Balloon Vinyl Macbook Decal', 14.00, 3.00, '', 'Banksy,Girl with Balloon,Sticker,Decal,Macbook', 5, '<p>Banksy Girl with Red Balloon. Inspired by world renowned graffiti artist Banksy.&nbsp; The decals are not limited to laptops, they can be applied to any smooth surface, for example fridge, door, or even your car.<br /><br />Our decal stickers are precision cut from our high grade self adhesive vinyl. For other sized decals please check out the categories links to the left.<br /><br /></p>', 1, '2011-05-18', 135, 1, ',,,,', '<p>Our decals are packaged in between two solid pieces of cardboard. They include a free practice decal so that you can get used to the application process.<br /><br />Since we are based in New Zealand the decals can sometimes take up to 2 weeks to arrive but dont worry they are well worth the wait.</p>', 1, 0);
