(333, 75, 'Bob-Omb inspired by Super Mario Bros - Amigurumi P', 80.00, 4.00, '', 'crochet toy,bobomb,super mario,amigurumi,nerdJERK', 1, '<p>This Bob-Omb is a Super Mario favourite. Almost every time someone sees one of these in my house, they start playing with him! Whether he''s blowing up the bad-guys or simply struttin'' his stuff, it''s a pleasure to play with his squishiness with your own hands.<br /><br />Bob-Omb has a body about 6" tall with a coiled 2" fuse that is supported by a pipe cleaner. You can pose his fuse any way you''d like (if the fuse is fully extended, the Bob-Omb measures about 10" from his toes to the top of the fuse). He also includes an awesome hand-crocheted turn key that really does turn, as to allow you the joy of winding him up and throwing him at your fave geek within your living room.&nbsp;<br /><br />Each turn key is crafted a little differently, as is the nature of handmade, so you can feel special in that every Bob-Omb is your own personal work of art!<br /><br />He''s crocheted over many hours out of super soft yarns and and stuffed evenly with hypoallergenic polyfill. His shoes are filled with individually embroidered muslin bags filled with poly-beads to give him some extra weight and allow him to stand on his own.<br /><br />A great gift for a geeky boyfriend, nerdy roommate or awesome friend!<br /><br />Although all parts are securely hand-sewn in, we wouldn''t recommend Bob-Omb play with children under 3.&nbsp;<br /><br />If you''d like him in another colour, just let me know and I''ll make a special posting (please allow 10-14 days to create your masterpiece).</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 1, '2011-05-29', 139, 1, ',,,promotion,', '<p>Shipping prices on Broodr.com reflect USPS First Class Shipment within the USA within 10-14 days of payment, as your item is MADE TO ORDER. Please contact for international shipping rates: nerdJERK@gmail.com</p>', 1, 0),
