(299, 182, 'M.A.D. Box - Tube Based 6 Channel Guitar Pedal Mix', 495.00, 35.00, '', 'steampunk,guitar,pedal,mixer,copper', 1, '<p>CopperGear is proud to present the M.A.D. Box. The Multisonous Amalgamation Device. A unique handmade tube based guitar pedal mixer. Never before has a guitarist had such control over their sound, be it on stage or in your garage. <br /><br />Simply plugin your guitar and up to six pedals into the M.A.D. Box then plug it into your amp or recording device and enjoy the freedom to mix, overlay, or layer to your hearts content. You will never need to record the same guitar track multiple times with different effects again. Side chain your pedals or mix down separate pedals independently. Layer your sounds like never before in realtime. Perfect for live gigs.<br /><br />For example: use one pedal to create a solid distortion and send it to the mix, now setup a delay pedal to echo your clean guitar tone and side chain it to a flanger then mix it all down. The possibilities to fiddle around with are endless. ;)<br /><br />With the tube, a 12AU7, being utilized as a pre amp and output stage amplifier you can get amazing warmth from your guitar. Use the pre amp stage to drive your pedals harder or even starve them to customize your sound even further. Even a 70''s era single coil pickup can sound like a powerhouse. The internal transistor based mixer is exceptionally quiet so all you hear is what you create. <br /><br />Each channel from the bottom up consists of:<br />a pedal input and output (2 x nickle plated 1/4 inch jack)<br />a side chain input and output (2 x nickle plated 1/4 inch jack)<br />an input toggle (to change input from either main guitar or side chain)<br />an output toggle (to change output from pedal to side chain)<br />and a channel volume control so you don''t have to affect the drive on some pedals by changing volume on the pedal.<br /><br />Main controls are:<br />main input and output for connecting guitar and amp/recording device (2 x nickle plated 1/4 inch jack)<br />input volume controls the pre amp volume of the guitar signal<br />output volume controls the overall output volume of the device<br /><br /><br />CopperGear strives to blend the old with the new, and the M.A.D. Box is no exception. We have taken great pains to re-create old style circuitry and sound by not using any IC''s (integrated circuits) in the audio path. Under certain circumstances the unit can pickup radio frequencies due to the old style circuitry. And just like old synthesizers and telephone switch boards we have used the tactile experience of 1/4in TS jumper cables for side chaining different channels together. And, in sticking to tradition, there is no injection molded plastic to be found. The entire device is handmade from wood, copper, brass, and steel to hopefully bring you decades of dependable operation.<br /><br />The M.A.D. Box is a culmination from years of suggestions, wishes, and dreams of hundreds of guitarists. <br /><br />Thank you all.<br /><br />The M.A.D. Box is finally here.<br /><br />All devices are hand made, tested, and numbered before shipping. Build time can take up to 3 weeks. <br /><br />Included with purchase:<br />6 x 1'' long 1/4" TS jumpers<br />1 x 12AU7 tube<br />1 x 15v center positive power supply<br />manual<br />Certificate of Authenticity<br /><br />If you live outside the United States please contact me prior to purchasing to validate your location and shipping charges.</p>\n<p>For more info visit <a href="http://copper-gear.blogspot.com/" target="_blank">CopperGear</a></p>', 1, '2011-08-06', 93, 5, ',,,,', '<p>Shipping:<br />US Priority Mail is used within the United States<br /><br />Returns/Exchanges:<br />Since all devices are not made until ordered, they are tested for functionality and quality before shipping. As a result returns/exchanges are not accepted. If a product is damaged during shipping please contact us immediately so we can begin the insurance process with the postal service.</p>', 1, 0),
(302, 71, 'Custom 8GB USB Flash Drive in original Lego Minifi', 149.95, 9.99, 'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cnCwCm8JVrE&NR=1', 'lego usb stick minifig,lego usb flash drive minifigure,lego usb drive minifig,lego datenstick minifigur,lego memory stick minifigure', 1, '<p>Handmade 8 GB USB HighSpeed Flash Drive in a original LEGO&reg; Minifigure (seen on pictures 4GB Version no difference in design to other GB Versions) The Dark Side of USB with feet protection cap<br /><br />YouTube Video<br />http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cnCwCm8JVrE<br /><br />+ (optional) MOBILE APPS (Applications/configuration (link to the pictures task bar) http://tinyurl.com/nnrljq<br /><br />included in delivery:<br />-8 GB HighSpeed flash memory in a original Lego&reg; Minifigure<br />-with feet protection cap<br />-laser sword<br />-chip passive cooling<br />-clickon magnet brick<br />-clickon showbrick<br />-custom made with professional equipment<br />-production in germany in small amounts<br />-great haptik (very emotional "feeling")<br />-Windows ME/2000/XP/Vista/7 and Mac OS 10.9x or above and Linux 2.4 and later compatible<br />-free optional Mobile Stick Applications/configuration (no installation on the pc)<br /><br />cost for shipping $ 9.99<br /><br />It&acute;s not a trick it&acute;s a stick :-)!<br /><br />T W I T T E R<br />Now i twitter ;-) -&gt; web find of the day and not to forget my passion usb in original Lego&reg; Bricks. If you want the newest informations about my products and a little bit fun or amazing finds in the web just follow me:<br /><br />https://twitter.com/databrick<br /><br />LEGO&reg; Brick and Knob configurations are trademarks of the LEGO&reg; group of companies, which does not sponsor, authorise or endorse this website or product.</p>', 0, '2011-06-24', 85, 5, ',,,,', '', 1, 0),
