st of these types of soaps.<br /><br />Each product is made in my home. I remain committed to using only high quality, vegan ingredients in my soap.<br /><br />You can find my soaps covered at Computer idee (Netherlands), GamePro, GamesMaster (Germany), GEE Magazine (Germany), Forbes, Liberating Style, Komo 4 News (Seattle) Micro Hebdo (France), Thrillist (Boston and Seattle), Wired UK, and WonkaVision. GamePro gave my soap the Editors'' Choice Award!<br /><br />SOCIAL NETWORK FTW:<br />http://twitter.com/DigitalSoaps<br />www.facebook.com/pages/DigitalSoaps/205525062068<br /><br /><strong>DigitalSoaps: Inventor of gamer, gadget and geek soap.&nbsp;</strong></p>', 1, '2011-05-25', 119, 11, ',,,,', '', 1, 0),
