(411, 61, 'Veggie-Peeler', 14.99, 0.00, '', 'Slice,Veggie-Peeler,Universal Design,,', 100, '<div class="product-body">\n<p><span style="font-size: small;">Recommended by the Cooking Club of America, the slice&trade; Veggie-Peeler features a super-sharp ceramic blade that lasts ten times longer than steel. Make quick work of peeling potatoes, carrots, cucumbers, soft foods like peaches, tomatoes, and slippery bell peppers -- even tough-skinned mangos. Ergonomic design fits comfortably in both small and large hands with a non-slip handle that''s light-weight to prevent fatigue. Ceramic blade is non-allergenic, chemically neutral, and impervious to acid, fat and salt. Won''t brown food, transfer smells, or leave a metallic taste.</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: small;">- Ceramic blade lasts longer than steel</span><br /><span style="font-size: small;"> - Stays sharp and never rusts</span><br /><span style="font-size: small;"> - Lightweight non-slip finish</span><br /><span style="font-size: small;"> - Built-in eyer</span><br /><span style="font-size: small;"> - Blade flips for left- and right-handers</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: small;">Design by Karim Rashid</span></p>\n</div>', 0, '2011-06-17', 122, 16, ',,,,', '', 1, 0),
(408, 66, 'Safety Cutter', 5.99, 0.00, '', 'Slice,Safety Cutter,Universal Design,,', 100, '<div class="product-body">\n<p><span style="font-size: small;">The Slice&trade; Safety Cutter is the most versatile tool you''ll ever own. Features a finger-friendly microscopic ceramic blade that''s quick, easy and a safe substitute for scissors or traditional safety knives. Slice Safety Cutters are perfect for scrap-booking, clipping recipes, coupons and news articles, removing shrink-wrap, opening CDs, DVDs, plastic packaging, and more. Includes a built-in magnet and key-ring hole.</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: small;">- Ceramic blade lasts longer than steel</span><br /><span style="font-size: small;"> - Stays sharp and never rusts</span><br /><span style="font-size: small;"> - Built-in magnet and key-ring hole</span><br /><span style="font-size: small;"> - Finger-Friendly&trade; Design</span><br /><span style="font-size: small;"> - For left- and right-handers</span></p>\n</div>', 0, '2011-06-16', 122, 16, ',,,,', '', 1, 0),
(410, 170, 'EXO10 Aluminum and Rosewood iPhone 4 Case', 155.00, 12.00, '', 'iPhone 4,iPhone,Metal case,phone case,hard case', 10, '<p>The EXOvault EXO10 is an amazing case. It is made from high quality aluminum and features a full, beautifully grained solid rosewood back. This is definitely an attention getter- I promise you people will oooh and awww! All of our EXOvault iPhone cases are handcrafted in our artist studios in Brooklyn, NY. ALL work is done by us from the initial design to proto-type to handfinished final product. We pay attention to every detail and stand behind our work! The aluminum EXO10 iPhone 4 case is available in silver, black, gray or bronze with rosewood. We can also make it with Ebony wood on the back so please check our other listings.</p>', 1, '2011-06-22', 148, 3, ',,,promotion,', '<div id="cboxLoadedContent" style="display: block; width: 840px; overflow: auto; height: 232px;">\n<div id="shipping-popup">\n<p>We make all of our cases according to order. We handcraft everything right here in our shop and pay attention to every detail. Quality takes time, and we will usually be able to create your iPhone case and ship it to you with in 2 weeks. Of course many orders, especially those in the US will be delivered much faster than that.</p>\n<p>We ship pretty much anywhere in the world. In the USA we use Priority Mail from the US Post Office and you will be able to track your package. In the USA the shipping rate is 12.00. Of course we will combine shipping on more than one case.</p>\n<p>We can use Priority Mail International for most of Europe, Canada and Japan (and some additional countries) no problem, the cost is 22.00. For some countries like Italy, Mexico, regions throughout the Middle East, Russia, Hungary and other areas of Eastern Europe we suggest you upgrade to Fed Ex or pay for trackable Express shipping via the US Post Office which will cost you 36.00. Fed Ex, UPS, DHS and others are available but range in price from 50 - 90.00 depending on country.</p>\n</div>\n</div>', 1, 0),
