(439, 23, 'Leantisserie', 24.99, 12.00, 'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KsxhosMGDmU', ',,,,', 100, '<p><span style="font-size: small;"><strong>The world''s first free-standing rotisserie inside an oven.</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: small;">Nutritional research suggests that meats cooked on a rotisserie are leaner and healthier than baking or frying. In basic terms: The fat drips right-off.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: small;">So place your main courses onto the Leantisserie and slide it into your oven set for broil. You&rsquo;re suddenly free while your meal is being cooked to perfection.Cook chicken, lamb, roasts, ribs, ham&hellip; even a fifteen-pound turkey!</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: small;">But the Leantisserie doesn''t stop there. Simply flip it and it becomes a self-rotating shish kabob roaster. Put your favorite meats and veggies onto the skewers for a phenomenal feast.And cleaning your Leantisserie couldn''t be easier. It goes right into the dishwasher.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: small;">You can also use the Leantisserie on your barbeque. No need to ever again flip burgers and hot dogs again. Spend quality time with your friends and family while the Leantisserie does all the work.The Leantisserie comes with an innovative two-way rotisserie rack, heavy-duty roasting rod, five shish kabob skewers and a control box.</span></p>', 0, '2011-06-28', 106, 9, ',,,,', '<p><span style="font-size: small;"><strong>Return Policies </strong></span><br /><span style="font-size: small;">Inventist, Inc. is dedicated to customer satisfaction. If your purchase does not fulfill your needs for any reason, you can return your item for an exchange or refund. Simply contact our store to receive instructions on returning your purchase. The following conditions apply:</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style="font-size: small;">All returns must be made within 30 days of purchase.</span></li>\n<li><span style="font-size: small;">It