(453, 39, 'Mini Skateboard Bottle Opener - Old School Pig', 10.00, 2.00, '', 'skater,skateboard,party gift,recycled,pop', 10, '<p><span style="font-size: small;">Our new Mini-decks are totally rad keychains made from Recycled Broken Skateboards cut into classic skate deck shapes! The Mini-deck also doubles as a bottle opener for "pop- top" bottles!</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: small;">The Mini-deck bottle opener is based on an old trick in which you open a "pop-top" bottle using a Bic lighter. If you are unfamiliar with this trick, opening a bottle with your Mini-deck may take some time to master. But like skateboarding, you must practice to get better! Also like a real skateboard, your Mini-deck will acquire scrapes and scars as it is used. </span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: small;">To open a bottle; Grip the bottle neck firmly, about 1/4" below the cap with one hand. With your Mini-deck in your opposite hand, GRIPTAPE UP, insert the nose of the deck in the 1/4" gap between your top finger gripping the bottle and the cap. Using your finger as the pivot point, and the Mini-deck as a simple lever, pry off the cap and enjoy! An instructional tag is included with every Mini-deck. There are many ways to pop a top using a Mini-deck, invent your own tricks!</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: small;">Mini-decks are made from real recycled skateboards, so every one is uniquely awesome. We will send you a random one with an Old School "Pig" shape when you order.</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: small;">This listing is for an Old School "Pig" shape Mini-deck with a 1 1/8" keyring.</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: small;">Approx. Size: 3" x 1" x 1/2"</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: small;">Finished with food safe mineral oil.</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: small;">Free Shipping if you buy more than one! (or purchase with any other deckstool product!)</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: small;">Please Contact us with any questions!</span></p>', 0, '2011-08-04', 151, 9, ',distributor,,promotion,', '', 1, 0),
