(462, 38, 'Recycled Seat Cushion for skateboard stool', 75.00, 5.00, '', ',,,,', 1, '<p><span style="font-size: small;">Don''t get us wrong, the deckstool is very comfortable. But sometimes you need a longer chill session, and stylish comfort is important...</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: small;">The New (almost) 100% recycled "Lid" seat cushion is the answer. The "Lid" is a high quality seat pad, specially sculpted to hug the contours of your deckstool seat and look cool doing it. </span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: small;">The upper material of the "Lid" cushion is canvas made from recycled plastic bottles and features our custom "Broken deck" print. </span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: small;">The lower material is recycled rubber from used automobile tires and functions to "grip" the deckstool seat preventing any "cushion drift" during use.</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: small;">The stuffing is made from reclaimed manufacturing scraps.</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: small;">Thread and grommets - Not recycled :(</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: small;">Size: 8"W x 13 1/2"L x 2"Tk.</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: small;">FREE SHIPPING with your deckstool order!</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: small;">Please contact us with any questions or if multiple cushions are needed. Thanks for looking!</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: small;">Jason </span><br /><span style="font-size: small;">Email: info [!at] deckstool.com</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: small;">www.deckstool.com</span></p>', 0, '2011-07-03', 151, 11, ',,,,', '<p>$10 shipping outside US</p>', 1, 0),
