(467, 27, 'The Slinkable', 30.00, 0.00, 'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kTmooE6tGBY', ',,,,', 99, '<p><span style="font-size: small;">Slinkable is a collection of flexible docking and syncing products that stand for your devices. This project started to bring the iPod and iPhones multi-touch color displays closer and more accessible to the user. This flexibility allows the screen of the device to work with the screen of the laptop to display content on the device while charging and syncing. </span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: small;">By combining the strength of a docking station and flexibility of a cable. Slinkable is a very lightweight device that is very portable and useful in many applications.</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: small;">- Docking and Syncing to a Computer</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: small;">- Charging with a USB type car charger (iPod and gps)</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: small;">- Charging on a wall outlet</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: small;">- Converts Directly to USB</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: small;">- Slinkable is made from flexible high grade silicone rubber and polycarbonate.</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: small;">Slinkables work with every iPod, iPhone, and iPod Touch. Because it is flexible it can accommodate these devices without the use of an adapter. In addition the microSync can be used as a stand alone iPod or iPhone stand. Slinkables are very portable and lightweight and the integrated stand can be adjusted to hold your devices in place with or without an available usb port.&nbsp; </span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: small;">Slinkables are designed to be adjustable and provide different uses that work for you.&nbsp; I''m exited to hear what you think of the device and the different ways it can be used to help you everyday. &nbsp;If possible I would like to produce this product with your help.</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: small;">I have created the 3D design and working prototypes are finished and tested. 3D printed prototypes will be completed and shown on KickStarter by the time the project ends and will be manufactured if the project goal is achieved.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: small;">After closing of this fund, if successful, Slinkables will be produced in a timely manner and then shipped to reward those who contributed to the success of the product.&nbsp; Please note that due to the nature of the design it may take some time before you receive shipment.&nbsp; This is to make a quality product that meets your expectations. Please note Slinkables is designed to be use while the laptop is on a flat surface.&nbsp; Slinkables are not designed to be moved or picked up while iPhone/iPod is connected to the USB port. &nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: small;">Slink-in to put your devices in-Sync!</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: small;">Slinkable Flexible USB with PowerPivot folding system.</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: small;">*Works with all iPods, and iPhones except iPod shuffle</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: small;">*iPhone and iPod not included</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: small;"><strong>Patents Pending</strong></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 0, '2011-07-07', 158, 15, 'manufacturer,distributor,funding,promotion,', '<p><span style="font-size: medium;">Shipping to Canada add $10, International add $15</span></p>', 1, 0),
