(646, 26, 'gameboy tube dress', 80.00, 4.00, 'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=izlumtjABO', 'gameboy,dress,nintendo,knit,', 5, '<p>i made this game dress from soft gray knit and black fabric. i gave it buttons and a screen just like a real game boy! each piece is sewn on separately. <br /><br /><br /><br />PLEASE SPECIFY SIZE WHEN CHECKING OUT. also your height so i can make it long enough!!!! thank you!<br /><br />size: bust waist hips<br />xsmall: 30 25 33<br />small: 32 27 34<br />medium: 34 29 36<br />large: 38 31 40<br />xlarge: 40 33 44</p>', 1, '2011-07-26', 174, 3, ',,,,', '<p>completion of dress may take up to 4 weeks. will be shipped via USPS.</p>', 1, 0),
(647, 27, 'Circuit bent Casio MT-35', 210.00, 15.00, 'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wc9h-6cCnDY', 'Circuit bent Casio,synth ,8bit,drone,unique', 1, '<p>Here is a one of a kind instrument for those who enjoy not only glitched out madness but also the wonderful stock Casio tones. It produces truly unique rhythms and tones.<br />It also has the option to work just like it did off the factory line. No effects No bends just that Casio goodness... now for the good stuff!<br />The bends include:<br />-An eight point patch bay that alters mostly the drums but also muffles other sounds and creates other effects when the chords switch is on.<br />-A two way switch that boost the bass chord tone two different ways<br />-Another two way switch that effects the bass tone in multiple ways<br />-Another two way switch that effects the regular keys... also in two different ways.<br />-Pitch/randomize knob with on/off switch.<br />-Filter/Mod/Fuzz knob... Kinda does what it does. Hard to explain but cool enough to make the final product!<br />-...Oh yeah, A Commodore 64 controller that is a break down for the drums. It''s button either turns the drums on or adds random tones depending on if the chord switch is on.<br />-1/4" Stereo, RCA, and its original headphone output... 1/4" and RCA work together with no signal loss, Headphone output only works solo. Speaker has been removed for the controller (C64)<br />-A reset switch(Ive had all the bends and patch bay filled with no crashes ever) but better safe then sorry.<br /><br />All the Bends sound great alone or together with various connections. It also has the option to get real glitchy and random too. Truly a great sounding instrument.</p>', 1, '2011-07-26', 74, 5, ',distributor,funding,promotion,', '<p>Item will be shipped via First class unless other wise stated. Other options avalable too.</p>', 1, 0),
(648, 33, 'Right Ear Wrap Around Stereo-to-mono Earphone', 19.95, 5.60, '', ',,,,', 10, '<h2>One Good Earbud mixes both channels of stereo audio devices into one ear.</h2>\n<p>One Good Earbud is the ideal way to safely listen to music, podcasts, audio books, and mobile calls while running, cycling, snowboarding, or working out at the gym. Our custom-designed earphone mixes both channels of audio, providing stereo quality sound through a single ear - enabling the wearer to maintain alertness in any environment.</p>\n<p>This product features a comfortable over-the-ear, non-slip soft rubber contoured attachment which holds the earpiece in place. This design is perfect for running, jogging, boating, hiking, camping, motorcycle rides, bicycling, spinning and dancing. For those who must maintain one ear open for communicating or hearing those around them, this earphone will be perfect for you.</p>\n<h2>Technical Specifications:<br /><br /></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Stereo 3.5mm plug (same as 1/8-inch size plug)<br /><br /></li>\n<li>Compatible with Apple iPods, Apple iPhone, Sony MP3 Players, Laptops and Desktop Computers, as well as Sansa, Creative, Etek, Ativa, RCA and other low-cost MP3 players.<br /><br /></li>\n<li>Works with any device with a stereo or mono 1/8-inch (1/8") or 3.5mm subminiature plug<br /><br /></li>\n<li>Works with all Stereo and Mono Audio Devices<br /><br /></li>\n<li>Great Bass Sound<br /><br /></li>\n<li>Product Weight: 0.4 ounces<br /><br /></li>\n<li>Design mixes Left and Right Stereo Channels Together into One Earpiece<br /><br /></li>\n<li>Cord Length: 42-inches long<br /><br /></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 1, '2011-07-27', 147, 5, ',,funding,promotion,', '<p>Products ship by USPS First Class or First Class International within 3 business days, from Arizona, USA.</p>', 1, 0),
